[1] Preventive measures, racing pigeons
Date: Sun 14 Apr 2013
Source: Sina.com [in Chinese, machine trans. summarised, edited]
http://news.sina.com.cn/c/2013-04-15/023926825162.shtml


Beijing's Pigeon Association recently issued a notice requiring all districts and counties to suspend all competitions. The Dongcheng District Pigeon Association said yesterday [13 Apr 2013] that in line with instructions by the district's animal health authorities, pigeon droppings should be treated by sanitary measures and the pigeons' facilities disinfected daily to prevent epidemics.

[Byline: Liu Jenny]

